  "3123670": {
    "name": "COMING HOME",
    "steam_appid": 3123670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/7b2e3c2eb61408d1be2007c8ae27cd14.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"COMING / HOME\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/1f8b000d1d8f063f7f310fb008328cff.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player aims their revolver at the Clown, who is about to attack the player with a hammer.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/1f8b000d1d8f063f7f310fb008328cff.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/1f8b000d1d8f063f7f310fb008328cff.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A retro slasher horror game, with a focus on home defense. In the dead of night, you hear someone lurking outside - but you are not defenseless. Watch the cameras, barricade your doors, and have your gun at the ready - anything to keep the Sundown Rippers from claiming their next victim. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >COMING HOME is a chilling fusion of survival horror and resource management. Inspired by the slasher classics of old, as well as gaming horror classics like Silent Hill and Five Nights at Freddy's, you must defend yourself with booby traps, an unreliable generator, and a rusty revolver - but the Rippers are cunning, and they'll catch on to your tricks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/89efcec1915d0c47963813142926a6ac.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"THIS ISN&#039;T A PUNISHMENT / IT&#039;S AN ASCENSION\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/357997be36015afc105147c2851a678a.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player is using the laptop. The laptop shows a camera feed of someone climbing through the window. The player presses a button, activating a shock trap on that window. The person climbing now falls down.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/357997be36015afc105147c2851a678a.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/357997be36015afc105147c2851a678a.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Douglas Nelson, elderly recent widower, whose children have all moved on. In the throes of loneliness, a bump in the night and a sinister phone call makes Douglas realize he's fallen under the gaze of the Sundown Rippers, a group of notorious serial killers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their leader looks just like the figure Doug's son often drew as a teenager... before he was found dead in an alley. Still haunted by the death of Frank Nelson and yearning for closure, Douglas must confront the Rippers and survive the worst night of his life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/3a370b20a53481a79c3ff5a57269645e.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"SURVIVAL HORROR / RESOURCE MANAGEMENT\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a2c2a405c65769f7c1b206edab12a8e1.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player is opening a generator control panel and flipping a switch.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a2c2a405c65769f7c1b206edab12a8e1.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a2c2a405c65769f7c1b206edab12a8e1.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sundown Rippers are persistent, and will do anything to have you at the other end of their blade. Using your home defense system, you must booby trap windows and scan for movement inside the house - but be wary of the power draining from your backup generator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're armed with a revolver as a last resort, but between your shaking aim and your dwindling ammunition... your odds aren't great. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/3b58eb54f8007ba8fda9319d8479e917.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"WHEN IT&#039;S SUNDOWN / NO ONE IS SAFE\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a02ddd4b21154bbf83bc7c4f7264ad4a.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player looks through a door frame and sees a masked woman. The player closes the door and barricades the door with a chair.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a02ddd4b21154bbf83bc7c4f7264ad4a.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/a02ddd4b21154bbf83bc7c4f7264ad4a.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No robots; no monsters; no ghosts. Just you and them. The Rippers are cunning, intelligent, and will catch on to your strategies if you aren't careful. They will taunt, misdirect, and take control of the things you must rely on to survive. Engage in a tense and stifling chess game, where the stakes are everything and your chances are close to nothing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/36bb02708c8fd337b0c0ceb37dc10bea.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"REWIND TO A TIME / DRENCHED IN BLOOD\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/210f4fef0429b36875eac7092b3de710.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player is walking through a hallway, when a man in a clown mask bursts through the door on the other end of the hallway.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/210f4fef0429b36875eac7092b3de710.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/210f4fef0429b36875eac7092b3de710.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The haunting chills of an 80s synth horror soundtrack by Aidan O'Flynn paint the experience of COMING HOME, combined with hand-crafted textures and models. The experience is accentuated by authentic shaders to replicate the visuals of a retro slasher film, with the UI tailored to fit the era. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/7aec61d645fa3fd931514209b4614af4.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"NO MORE CHAINS / NO MORE MEMORIES\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/414012298ae8d37e75f7f3569d47f6b7.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player walks up to a bloody note and inspects it. A menu appears, showing a transcript and visual description of the note.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/414012298ae8d37e75f7f3569d47f6b7.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/414012298ae8d37e75f7f3569d47f6b7.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Mementos to confront the past of an unreliable narrator, and discover Evidence to learn the history of the Sundown Rippers' murder spree. In-game documents, mysterious phone calls, and environmental storytelling are key to piecing together the rot within the Nelson household, and the ties that bind them to the Sundown Rippers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/981f1336a0d471254e4f6d200f98451b.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"A NIGHTMARE / EVERYONE CAN EXPERIENCE\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/5c3460fdc11d879098913655fa644305.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; Two accessibility features are presented. First, Directional Closed Captioning is shown in action. Then, high-contrast mode is presented by showing how the game looks with this mode off and on.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/5c3460fdc11d879098913655fa644305.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/5c3460fdc11d879098913655fa644305.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accessibility options allow for a customizable experience for anyone brave enough to confront the Rippers. Directional closed captioning, high-contrast visuals, VHS effect toggles, game speed sliders, extensive control options, document transcripts, and more will ensure the Rippers can take their violent murder spree to anyone who crosses their path - they aren't picky. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/82d5e3789414c13065095dc729bd9c17.webp?t=1769903412\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/82d5e3789414c13065095dc729bd9c17.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"IN YOUR MIND / IN YOUR HEART / IN YOUR HOME\" width=780 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/f78d68f8d1256c8c6c6021af7d0a1ead.poster.avif?t=1769903412\" aria-label=\"Gameplay footage; The player is standing in their garage-turned office, in front of their desk. The lights are off but slowly dim on, revealing that a man in a rooster mask is standing across the room. As the man slowly walks towards the player, the lights flicker and then turn off again.\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/f78d68f8d1256c8c6c6021af7d0a1ead.webm?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/f78d68f8d1256c8c6c6021af7d0a1ead.mp4?t=1769903412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123670/extras/268d4e2b2e77278f6a2829537b81d32f.avif?t=1769903412\" alt=\"GET READY, DOUGLAS\" width=1560 height=80 /></span></p>",
